            <h3 class="featured-project-title">Thai Numeral Converter</h3>
            <p class="featured-project-desc">Automated utility for Thai government documentation, converting Arabic to Thai numerals while preserving email addresses and URLs.</p>
            <div class="project-tags"><span class="project-tag">Utility</span><span class="project-tag">Localization</span></div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="featured-project-slide" aria-hidden="true">
          <a href="project/bnk48/" target="_blank" class="featured-project-media-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
            <div class="featured-project-media">
              <img src="project/bnk48/bnk48-thumb.webp" alt="BNK and CGM48 election predictive analysis notebook preview" loading="lazy" width="1400" height="1161">
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="project/bnk48/" target="_blank" class="featured-project-copy-link" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <div class="featured-project-copy">
            <div class="featured-project-kicker">Kaggle Notebook</div>
