            <p class="featured-project-desc">Technical case study using end-to-end ML (Scraping to Prediction) to forecast election outcomes in the entertainment industry.</p>
            <div class="project-tags"><span class="project-tag">Machine Learning</span><span class="project-tag">Web Scraping</span><span class="project-tag">Prediction</span></div>
            </div>
          </a>
